---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Smart Holiday Shopping Strategies">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 sm:py-12">
    {/* Hero Section */}
    <div class="relative mb-8 sm:mb-12">
      <img 
        src="/images/blog/holiday-savings.jpg"
        alt="Holiday Shopping Strategies"
        class="w-full h-[300px] sm:h-[500px] object-cover rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl shadow-lg"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-4 sm:p-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-2 sm:mb-4 leading-tight">
          Smart Holiday Shopping Strategies
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-200 text-base sm:text-lg mb-2">Published on December 9, 2024</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Article Content */}
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      {/* Introduction */}
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6 sm:mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        The holiday season doesn't have to break the bank. With smart planning and strategic shopping, you can find great gifts for everyone on your list while staying within your budget.
      </p>

      {/* Main Content Sections */}
      <div class="space-y-8 sm:space-y-12">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
            Plan Your Shopping Strategy
          </h2>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-primary/10 rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-8">
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mr-3">1</span>
                <span>Create a detailed gift list with budgets</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mr-3">2</span>
                <span>Research prices early to spot good deals</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mr-3">3</span>
                <span>Sign up for retailer newsletters</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mr-3">4</span>
                <span>Follow brands on social media for exclusive offers</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
            Time Your Purchases
          </h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Best Shopping Days</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Black Friday deals</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Cyber Monday sales</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Early bird specials</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Price Tracking</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Use price comparison tools</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Set price drop alerts</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Monitor historical prices</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
            Maximize Your Savings
          </h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white shadow-sm rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-6 border border-gray-100">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 sm:mb-3">Stack Discounts</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base">Combine coupons with sales and cashback offers</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white shadow-sm rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-6 border border-gray-100">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 sm:mb-3">Loyalty Programs</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base">Use reward points and member benefits</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white shadow-sm rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-6 border border-gray-100">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 sm:mb-3">Gift Cards</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base">Buy discounted gift cards for extra savings</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
            Online Shopping Tips
          </h2>
          <ul class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-6 space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Use shopping portals for extra cashback</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Install price comparison extensions</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Check multiple retailers for best prices</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Look for free shipping offers</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
            Avoid Common Pitfalls
          </h2>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-primary/10 rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-8">
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mr-3">!</span>
                <span>Don't fall for "limited time" pressure tactics</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mr-3">!</span>
                <span>Compare prices across multiple stores</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mr-3">!</span>
                <span>Read return policies carefully</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mr-3">!</span>
                <span>Watch out for shipping costs</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        {/* Conclusion */}
        <div class="mt-8 sm:mt-12 p-4 sm:p-8 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl">
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            With these smart holiday shopping strategies, you can enjoy the season of giving without the financial stress. Remember to plan ahead, compare prices, and take advantage of all available discounts and rewards programs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Custom styling for better visual hierarchy */
  .prose h2 {
    @apply font-display;
    scroll-margin-top: 100px;
  }
  
  .prose p {
    @apply leading-relaxed text-gray-600;
  }

  .prose ul {
    @apply my-4 sm:my-6;
  }

  .prose li {
    @apply text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base;
  }

  /* Smooth scroll behavior for anchor links */
  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }

  /* Better touch targets on mobile */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .prose li {
      @apply py-1;
    }
    
    .prose a {
      @apply py-2;
    }
  }
</style>
